---
title: Orange Cranberry Oatmeal with Pistachios, Cherry Drizzle, Chocolate Chips & Orange Wedges
description: Name a breakfast more comforting or filling than a hot, hearty bowl of oatmeal (...we’ll wait). Ready to make it irresistible? Simmer the oats with dried cranberries, orange zest, and cherry jam; then top it with a creamy cherry drizzle, nutty pistachios, and rich chocolate chips, plus juicy orange wedges on the side—the perfect formula for a yummy morning. The best part? This delicious, wholesome bowl comes together in a quick 15 minutes! After digging in, you’ll be fueled up and ready to take on the day.
